{"type": "article", "id": 29900, "title": "DIY 凉鞋", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-20T23:04:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160720211249f4tW0PMD6NxTogKF.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>凉鞋在夏天可是一件必不可少的装备，如果你觉得市面上的款式都不能标榜自己的个性，不妨来看看设计师 Sara Gulyas 推出的 DIY 凉鞋 <a href=\"http://pikkpack.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pikkpack</a>。Pikkpack 原本是 Gulyas 的毕业设计，她通过一次成功的众筹将它转变成了初创的时尚品牌。Gulyas 的设计灵感来源于匈牙利的 bocskor 鞋，这种鞋子仅由一整块皮革缝制而成，她将 DIY 属性与传统凉鞋结合，变成了既时尚又充满动手趣味的单品。这是它的<a href=\"http://pikkpack.com/products/pikkpack-flat-packed-leather-lace-up-sandal#shoe-upper-colour=brown&amp;shoelace-colour=reflective-blue&amp;sole-material-colour=yellow\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 89 美元，每个部件都有丰富的颜色可选。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720211305DxhWF0MgQLRV49ku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498778\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720211305wqND1HY4eys82chA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720211304pZYKsA9G6kxPv0ed.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160720211304aXVS0BsC8mbl5rMq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}